The Telegraph - Calcutta : Entertainment

 STYLE FILE

 AMRITA ARORA on what's on her mind and body

Favourite outfit: Blue jeans and white T-shirt

 Favourite outfit when driving to a shoot: Tracks and a T-shirt

 Favourite evening wear: A nice formal dress maybe a lovely salwar suit or a sari

 Favourite clubwear: Anything from jeans to a short skirt. If the party is at a friends place, jeans with a cute top

 Favourite nightwear: Pyjamas and a ganji

 Favourite designers: Vikram Phadnis, Manish Malhotra, Seema Khan, Gucci, Chanel

 Favourite brands: Gucci, Top Shop, River Island

 Favourite brand of jeans : True Religion, Seven, Stella McCartney

 Fetishes: Watches everything from a Rolex to a Swatch. Shoes 150 pairs. Sneakers from Schekers is a favourite

 Favourite shoe brand: Jimmy Choo, Todds

 Best dressed man in Bollywood: Saif Ali Khan he has a very cool sense of style

 Most expensive dress: A Roberto Cavalli dress

 Favourite perfume: Forever by Dior... using it forever

 Tip on fashion: Dress according to your personality

 Tip on make-up and hair care : Follow the KISS theory... Keep it simple, stupid

 Anita Raheja-Heena Agarwal (Bollywood News Service) 




